name: Roy Baharav
note:
Product: A speech enhancement technology that isolates a speech while eliminating all background noise, delivering voice recognition accuracy. It enables restaurants to upgrade their Drive-Thru instantly.

Country- Location: Tel Aviv, Israel.

Immediate Requirement: Chat Manager with a good writing English skills- reliable person.

For 2 shifts/7 days per week:

5am-5pm

10am-10pm 

6 hours per shift - Full time 3-4 people.

Next Step: Interview with candidates(3-5 candidates individually). 

Next Contact Date: On Thursday, (14.01.21) at 11:30 pm (our time).

ophir@hi.auto will also be present on the call.

Hi Auto-Interview

Every candidate got the same task: Short shared video with a meat booking and candidates had to catch the words and write it down into the Google document. 

Dariana (ID 819) - https://rh-s.com/marketer/content-managers/dariana-d/
26 y.o.,Odessa, and she is working in marketing sphere since 2013. Her previous work experience was a marketing project manager in the “Smart Agency” Company.

Olha (ID 706) - https://rh-s.com/marketer/lead-generation-managers/olha-r/
Fired after the call.

Maria (ID 486) - https://rh-s.com/marketer/lead-generation-managers/mariia-s/
18 y.o., Lviv. She is currently studying at the University and for a few days is training in the content department.

Olesia (ID 849) - https://rh-s.com/lead-generation-managers/olesia-y/
She had an experience of working the waiter and currently she is looking for Influencers’ contacts in various social networks.
English skills are quite good.

Myroslava (ID 753) - https://rh-s.com/lead-generation-managers/myroslava-t/
She has an experience of writing the texts, blogs, posts, descriptions, translation of texts for the site, copywriting.
She is a Lead Generation Manager now.

Daria (ID 883) - https://rh-s.com/marketer/lead-generation-managers/daria-y/
It's her first interview. She's graduated from the Academy of municipal administration a year ago. Now she is a Lead Generation Manager.

Juliana 24 y.o.
Her tasks are: potential leads' searching, CRM management, communication with clients.

And also Anna (ID 908)
There was also her first interview meeting.21 y.o., Lead Generation Manager.

Roy liked Olesya, Daria, Dariana and Maria. Girls made the same mistakes, like: instead of the word "meal" they've heard "menu" and in place of "bottled" they wrote "bottle". It can influence their understanding of the conversation, so Roy decided to make one more task for them.

Next call: Monday, 18 at 4 pm.
Hi Auto-Remote Helpers

We've discussed the result of the test tasks for the following candidates:
Dariana (ID 819), Maria (ID 486), Myroslava (ID 753), Daria (ID 883), Anna (ID 908) and Valeria (ID 828). 
The best results showed: Maria (ID 486), Daria (ID 883) and Anna (ID 908).

Next steps: Next week we are going to discuss their tasks and working hours. Also, they are going to hire 1-2 more candidates for this project.

Next contact day: Possibly Tuesday, Ophir will send an invitation and a schedule.

Anna Ovcharuk and Ophir Hacohen/Daria Yakhno and Ophir Hacohen (Hi Auto Company). meeting 26.01.21

We've interviewed Anna and Daria today. Both meeting was in zoom at 12pm and 1pm our time.

Anna's 23y.o. 
She've got Master's degree in language and a literature sphere.  She has an experience working in marketing and advertising compaings.
Ophir has sent a test for Anna to see how she will handle it online. It was too quick and noizy record for Anna and it's influenced the results. 
Ophir liked Anna, because she has a good English skills. But Anna doesn't match to this position, because of difficulties with understanding of native speakers' speach. 

At 1 pm Daria's been interviewed.
Daria's 23 y.o.
She has an experience of working in a restraunt sphere and she understood most of the speach from the records, so she can clearly understand the working process and can manage it.

Next steps:
27.01.21 at 1 pm we'll interview the following candidate- Maria Soroka and will understand with whom we'll move forward.
In the end of the week we'll discuss the future tasks for Daria (883) and will decide about the candacy of Maria.
In addition, Ophir said that they've prepared few hours of training for girls, Ophir will help the girls to get into things. During this time we can propose more candidates that will possible suit them too.

Mariia Soroka and Ophir Hacohen (Hi Auto) meeting (28.01.21)

We discussed the position Maria's been interviewed and tested before.

The tasks were following:
1) To listen a short conversation and mark the order in the audio from the proposed variants in the document (https://docs.google.com/document/d/1tBOCDM_cAkd4C2Y9VfYtPAh8fG-33yLPVgQZFnqtBMw/edit?usp=sharing).
2) To write down the second 2 min conversation in the chat.

Maria had some difficulties with the recognition of the words in the record.
So she isn't anfit candidate for this position.

Results: From all the candidates passed the task an appropriate one is Daria (ID 883). Next week we are going to interview Hanna (ID 755).
Ohir: Please, feel free to propose more candidates. So next week we can make a final decicsion and sign a contract.

LAST FOLLOW UP EMAIL 23 09 22

Comment: "Client is interested in a remote marketing expert".
Product: Digital marketing agency
Services Provided: They have 2 businesses. The first, Internet Center. It is a marketing consulting company specializing in Digital and Innovation.

They are driven by the excitement of creating marketing strategies combining cutting-edge technologies, and cost-effective solutions for organizations, companies, and brands.
Their mission is to help businesses evolve in gaining more customers, increasing sales, building brands and creating their unique digital presence. 
The second one, digital marketing agency. That is a startup in the fashion industry. 
They need to reach out clients about their services. Email doesn’t work for them. They want to try direct calls.
Country-Location: Israel
Target Audience: fashion industry, clients, who interested in such services
Immediate Requirement: LG manager who can speak directly to clients by call. The candidates should be without accent with good English and sales management skills.
Anat wants to try a part-time option to see how it works for her.
Next Step: Send CVs of most suitable candidates, price and all necessary information by email.
Next Contact Date: Interview will be tomorrow at 12.30.
anat@internetcenter.co.il

28.04.2021

WordPress developers:

Web developer, can work with Photoshop, Figma, HTML, Sas. Also she works with wordpress.

Web developer.

React developers:

Web developer. Work with HTML, SCS, Java script, React, Vanilla React. 

Aleksandr https://rh-s.com/front-end-developer/oleksandr-i/
Web developer. Work with ukrainian payment system. Can work with EPI, Data BAse. Know how to work with React. 


Lead generation managers:

She worked as an interpreter for 9 years. Now she is working as a Lead Generator Manager for 7 month.

Worked in a bank. Now is working as a Lead Generator Manager. 

What about lead generator manager, Anat like Olena. She wants to start with her in 05.05 (part-time). 
As for Developers, Sergey is the best one. Anat says that he is the most experienced guy. But she wants to see his works, so Sergey should send an example of apps, which he created.


We interviewed candidates for the Internet Center company.

React developers:

During the call Sergii shares his screen and shows their work and in detail tells how he did it and what tools were used. 
After that Anat tells what she wants Sergii to do. Anat asked if Sergii is familiar with Wordpress.  She will send a material and requirement for Sergii. If he is familiar with this requirement, another call will be with her CTO.
